 transaction fee through this gold trading app.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-grid wp-container-core-group-is-layout-b757edec wp-block-group-is-layout-grid\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading wp-container-content-5f6a1c15\" style=\"line-height:0.5\">Client<br><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"line-height:0.5\">Industry<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"line-height:0\">\n<p style=\"line-height:0\">Everest Gold (Singapore)<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p style=\"line-height:0\">Fintech<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-grid wp-container-core-group-is-layout-b757edec wp-block-group-is-layout-grid\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"line-height:0.5\">Platform<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"line-height:0.5\">Year<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"line-height:1\">\n<p>iOS and Android app<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p style=\"line-height:1.1\">2020<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-grid wp-container-core-group-is-layout-b757edec wp-block-group-is-layout-grid\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"line-height:0\">Tools<\/h3>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-94363411 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--20)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"207\" src=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Tools-logo-2-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-437\" style=\"width:315px;height:auto\" srcset=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Tools-logo-2-1.png 960w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Tools-logo-2-1-300x65.png 300w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/Tools-logo-2-1-768x166.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-30ab590f54076378faa854b2c04a03bb\" style=\"color:#264990\">My Role<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.8\">To collaborate with product manager and developers as to identify and resolve usability issues, revamp the app\u2019s user experience, deliver a modern UI redesign and launching new features. These improvements boosted conversion rates and enhanced user satisfaction.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"line-height:1.8\">Design Strategy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"line-height:1.8\">Information Architecture<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"line-height:1.8\">User Flow<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"line-height:1.8\">Product Design<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"line-height:1.8\">UX\/UI design<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-ffb0a08830f983f0b7185430213a73b6\" style=\"color:#264990\">Problem<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.8\">Based on the users\u2019 feedbacks during beta test, we uncovered several pain points and frustrations experienced by users:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul style=\"line-height:1.8\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">User feel confuse on Over-the-Counter (OTC) platform<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">Newbie traders have difficulties on how to start trading<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"line-height:1.8\">Users feel time consuming to reach customer service when have enquiry and they don\u2019t know where to contact customer service when hotline engaged<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-d0c80bd76eb33f9a03119837e69ea046\" style=\"color:#264990\">Define the Problem<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.6\">How might we improve the overall trading experience of the app and redesign a better OTC experience?<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Competitive Analysis<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.7\">We conducted competitive analysis of Etoro, Houbi, Hello Gold, and Xtrend to evaluate competitor strengths and weaknesses, focusing on:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul style=\"line-height:1.8\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Mobile app strategy<\/strong>: approach to user acquisition and engagement<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Feature set<\/strong>: key tools, functions, and differentiators<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Customer experience<\/strong>: workflows, ease of navigation, and support accessibility<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Design &amp; layout<\/strong>: visual hierarchy, UI consistency, and usability<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"269\" data-id=\"99\" src=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Competitor-logo-2-1024x269.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-99\" srcset=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Competitor-logo-2-1024x269.png 1024w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Competitor-logo-2-300x79.png 300w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Competitor-logo-2-768x202.png 768w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Competitor-logo-2.png 1210w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Persona<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"line-height:1.8\">Our target user is between age 25-50 years old who have stable income and would like to invest as another source of income. Investing the savings can help them to grow their wealth significantly over time instead of earning the interests in bank which even not enough to keep up with inflation over time.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1544\" data-id=\"101\" src=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Persona_EG.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-101\" srcset=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Persona_EG.png 1280w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Persona_EG-249x300.png 249w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Persona_EG-849x1024.png 849w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Persona_EG-768x926.png 768w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Persona_EG-1273x1536.png 1273w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-582a9e00bd587f253a846a0d7b2e6609\" style=\"color:#264990\">Design Decisions<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Redesign OTC Trading<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-open-sans-font-family\" style=\"line-height:1.8\">Besides real-time trading, Everest Gold offers an Over-the-Counter (OTC) trading feature designed for users without deposits on the platform or those wishing to trade in other currencies. OTC trading enables payments to be completed outside the platform, giving buyers and sellers the flexibility to choose the payment method that works best for both parties before finalizing a transaction.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Before:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul style=\"line-height:1.8\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">No clear indication of where users were in the OTC process<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">Difficult for buyers\/sellers to report issues during transactions<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">Key details were cumbersome to copy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);line-height:1.8\">Layout lacked visual hierarchy, causing confusion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\">After:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul style=\"line-height:1.8\" class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Step indicator<\/strong> clearly shows transaction progress and status<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Direct complaint button<\/strong> enables immediate issue reporting<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Copy icon<\/strong> for quick, error-free detail sharing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\"><strong>Streamlined layout<\/strong> improves clarity and user flow<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"background-color:#f5f5f5;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1210\" height=\"829\" data-id=\"107\" src=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Buy-Flow-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-107\" style=\"border-top-color:#f5f5f5;border-top-width:16px;border-right-style:none;border-right-width:0px;border-bottom-color:#f5f5f5;border-bottom-width:16px;border-left-style:none;border-left-width:0px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Buy-Flow-1.png 1210w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Buy-Flow-1-300x206.png 300w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Buy-Flow-1-1024x702.png 1024w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Buy-Flow-1-768x526.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1210px) 100vw, 1210px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-normal-font-size\"> Existing OTC Buy Flow<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"background-color:#f5f5f5\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border wp-duotone-unset-5\" style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1210\" height=\"1113\" src=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Sell-Flow-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-108\" style=\"border-style:none;border-width:0px;border-radius:0px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Sell-Flow-1.png 1210w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Sell-Flow-1-300x276.png 300w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Sell-Flow-1-1024x942.png 1024w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Existing_Sell-Flow-1-768x706.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1210px) 100vw, 1210px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-normal-font-size\" style=\"line-height:1.8\"> Existing OTC Sell Flow<br>To view larger image, click<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1WlgDVlJ9iPhvPVcs9VOI_3uENfosGxQk\/view?usp=drive_link\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/drive.google.com\/file\/d\/1WlgDVlJ9iPhvPVcs9VOI_3uENfosGxQk\/view?usp=drive_link\">&nbsp;here<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-additional-color has-alpha-channel-opacity has-additional-background-color has-background is-style-wide\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);margin-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60)\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"background-color:#f5f5f5;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1210\" height=\"1617\" data-id=\"124\"