ately after registration to help new users quickly understand how to start trading<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">Covered the basics of spot trading, including how to buy and sell gold and how instant profits can be achieved<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li style=\"padding-bottom:0;line-height:1.8\">Made tutorials accessible anytime in the Help Centre for returning users to review at their convenience<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group has-background is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"background-color:#f5f5f5;padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-8 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full has-custom-border\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1210\" height=\"1621\" data-id=\"122\" src=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/User-Flow-Buy-Sell-Tutorial.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-122\" style=\"border-top-color:#f5f5f5;border-top-width:16px;border-right-style:none;border-right-width:0px;border-bottom-color:#f5f5f5;border-bottom-width:16px;border-left-style:none;border-left-width:0px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/User-Flow-Buy-Sell-Tutorial.png 1210w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/User-Flow-Buy-Sell-Tutorial-224x300.png 224w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/User-Flow-Buy-Sell-Tutorial-764x1024.png 764w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/User-Flow-Buy-Sell-Tutorial-768x1029.png 768w, http:\/\/shuzhen-portfolio.local\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/User-Flow-Buy-Sell-Tutorial-1147x1536.png 1147w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1210px) 100vw, 1210px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-normal-font-size\">User Flow: Buy &amp; Sell T